{"header":"<h1>Parameter <code><span>StatLogger.S</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Stats","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"StatLogger","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"S","href":"#","kind":"argument-1"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-id\"><a href=\"#val-id\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> id : string</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Unique logger id, must be the same between all runs</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-stat\"><a href=\"#type-stat\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> stat</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>The type of stats being saved. For example:</p><ul><li>A stat aggregate <a href=\"../../index.html#type-t\" title=\"t\"><code>int t</code></a> or <a href=\"../../index.html#type-t\" title=\"t\"><code>float t</code></a> (in which case <a href=\"#val-combine\"><code>combine</code></a> is just <a href=\"../../index.html#val-concat\" title=\"concat\"><code>fun _ -&gt; concat</code></a>)</li><li>A record of such stat aggregates (<a href=\"#val-combine\"><code>combine</code></a> is then the field-wise <a href=\"../../index.html#val-concat\"><code>concat</code></a>)</li><li>A list of values (<a href=\"#val-combine\"><code>combine</code></a> is then <code>List.concat</code>)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-combine\"><a href=\"#val-combine\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> combine : <span>string <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-stat\">stat</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-stat\">stat</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"#type-stat\">stat</a></span></code></div></div>"}